/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yona Knight-Wisdom\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yona_Knight-Wisdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medals will be at stake in the men's discus throw where Roje\\u00a0Stona, Traves Smikle and Ralford Mullings will create history with three men in the final.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 478, \"end\": 491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traves_Smikle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Traves Smikle\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traves_Smikle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Traves_Smikle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will hope to take it a step further by winning a medal, joining Rajindra Campbell who won bronze in the men's shot put earlier.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"score\": 0.9999998963955985, \"rank\": 1.0360435025466114e-07, \"text\": \"Campbell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Campbell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Men's high jumper Romaine Beckford, 800m runner Navasky Anderson and three women's sprint hurdlers Danielle Williams, Ackera Nugent and Janeek Brown will make their first appearance in the morning session.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"score\": 0.9998269846818894, \"rank\": 0.00017304525751563846, \"text\": \"Beckford\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jermaine_Beckford\"}, {\"begin\": 753, \"en